"},{"pid":"199cf562c45c57b6bf62f6f63accbe4a7664febb","tid":276772,"uid":1779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"係連登講環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e95a661e5bd69a0a15ebad6de43e97cbccab46","tid":276772,"uid":23473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:27:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經去信幾間火鍋店，希望商戶到十一月才向顧客推介火鍋。<br />\n<br />\n叫人食幾個月西北風？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n環保蟹角幫佢地交租"},{"pid":"97b744137439650d0ab315a1f2695c26492e8e48","tid":276772,"uid":45160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:28:37.000Z","msg":"屌啦 d 仆街商場凍到雪房咁"},{"pid":"86fc92b90e81955d6271d931709a3cee8bc8d0ca","tid":276772,"uid":1059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:37:54.000Z","msg":"食冰啦屌你老母環保撚"},{"pid":"2fd062fcb83ae354c4c87b017cf1e61fb908d822","tid":276772,"uid":116359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:39:31.000Z","msg":"成個logic好有問題<br />\n話唔環保冬天食都係唔環保架啦<br />\n根本就係話唔好開冷氣<br />\n咁撚多籍口"},{"pid":"9fb8956c440f4eec27a2fc2fa3779fe9460a8caa","tid":276772,"uid":24696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:45:59.000Z","msg":"其實佢理念上都岩<br />\n不過根過不切實際<br />\n咁樣即係叫人唔好做生意<br />\n班老細員工係咪環保撚養？"},{"pid":"bdbb3a488ce3f919a18667010e0aab15fd306747","tid":276772,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T07:50:21.000Z","msg":"其實佢無講錯喎，佢都係想提高環保個意識姐"},{"pid":"44d2664341292f60de71b72221f028b497a84a3c","tid":276772,"uid":69096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實佢無講錯喎，佢都係想提高環保個意識姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好地地睇到呢個post<br />\n正常人都應該覺得係環保組織啱<br />\n加上佢講吓姐，又唔係實際禁止大家呢個行為<br />\n屌到好似殺人父母咁<br />\n連登真係好撚奇怪"},{"pid":"fd60feff46f54842c97511015ca77c430b883248","tid":276772,"uid":44593,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關你撚事咩屌你老母 <span style=\"color: red;\">咁專做打邊爐D鋪頭點撚算呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 賣雪糕火鍋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做生意就係有風險<br />\n食正條水就發到豬頭<br />\n咁萬一真係強制性要你咁環保唔比開鋪，就係佢地做生意要蝕嘅錢<br />\n<br />\nbtw你班連登仔突然咁關心人地火煱店生意，人地白交租，做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府出辣招阻止人炒樓，你當時又唔關心吓各位炒家會唔會無飯開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更何況個環保團體都係呼籲吓啫"},{"pid":"a54c2c3a45611105039cec82dff0e08323da8654","tid":276772,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:15:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就咁睇好似好煩膠<br />\n但係呢個又幾合理<br />\n開冷氣開到凍一凍打邊爐係幾浪費能源幾反智既</blockquote><br />\n你有享受到個冷氣，即係有用到啦<br />\n有用到即係冇浪費啦，邊有反智<br />\n<br />\n根本啲能源慳咗都會比其他人浪費架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n環保撚根本係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baff85564f4639a3973fffa283768014451fa2cb","tid":276772,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"大熱天時食火煱都唔正常得去邊啦"},{"pid":"9f44a2c206add7da950f8ca0adaf3a389a04db9c","tid":276772,"uid":13667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"唔比人做生意，好撚惡<br />\n<br />\n佢地寫字樓有冇裝冷氣"},{"pid":"c12e43d5bfa7b832889d7a56ce3d3d163be49cec","tid":276772,"uid":119347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"支那工廠日日排咁撚多廢氣唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a9e42c6adf618b26d4708f0b9a9c46d9eb5424","tid":276772,"uid":32414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:51:22.000Z","msg":"2009年8月16日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209b3c1bceea500e22394f3124319d3e759f63d7","tid":276772,"uid":51021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:59:33.000Z","msg":"on9 其實同你去餐廳食一樣 只不過打邊爐係拎出廚房煮"},{"pid":"09c7cbcb52e0a35b85a04ae1276938da25c4d05e","tid":276772,"uid":95096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就咁睇好似好煩膠<br />\n但係呢個又幾合理<br />\n開冷氣開到凍一凍打邊爐係幾浪費能源幾反智既</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次又幾啱邏輯"},{"pid":"4d225d4e8fdd8f70a4f2d39808ed1f59445b0052","tid":276772,"uid":107461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53512f2e21c54a18a1eff9059e7717c6cc88ed99","tid":276772,"uid":807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:21:01.000Z","msg":"環保撚真係好撚煩<br />\n<br />\n又話咪撚開冷氣？屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/172059_c87e32a46168a2ff835e9ea504a3c203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F172059_c87e32a46168a2ff835e9ea504a3c203.jpg&h=f9ecbdda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79dc75e3e868649f4771627af80ab8fe228e4da0","tid":276772,"uid":13831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>環保觸覺發現部份火鍋店，把冷氣溫度調至得十多度，有客人要著外套和披肩。環保觸覺批評，市民在炎夏開冷氣吃火鍋，浪費能源，已經去信幾間火鍋店，希望商戶到十一月才向顧客推介火鍋。天文台高級科學主任莫慶炎指，由七月至今，有九日氣溫錄得高達三十三度。而今年七月份平均溫度是29.1度，比過往高了0.4度，呼籲市民節約能源，避免氣候變暖問題繼續惡化。</blockquote><br />\n未到七月喎，咁快走上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f800afb6583b8877fd5374569b5d1a0d75e55a5c","tid":276772,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:27:04.000Z","msg":"只有政府政策立法先有用<br />\n得果少數人做有撚用咩<br />\n冇任何誘因真係彩你都on9<br />\n你班環保撚睇住人地開冷氣舒舒服服<br />\n你地自己受熱受苦把啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0255306d781300a4a3afe62c0f2b1fbb124d649","tid":276772,"uid":51233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就咁睇好似好煩膠<br />\n但係呢個又幾合理<br />\n開冷氣開到凍一凍打邊爐係幾浪費能源幾反智既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你當打邊爐係取暖既手段先會係反智<br />\n繼打邊爐下一個目標就係燒肉、燒味、鐵板個類野野"},{"pid":"56a54fd21ab2d045b8d28461821a0a95344118b2","tid":276772,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:34:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f10c9cd73e94d97c3eb504fcea98f57c91091bc7","tid":276772,"uid":98143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最好你環保觸覺唔好俾人影到你地office開冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直情應該搭車都唔可以搭有冷氣果D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行路啦!</blockquote><br />\n搭電車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e8c1f402cd7864eca05d6f8ff1a1d32354e07d","tid":276772,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最好你環保觸覺唔好俾人影到你地office開冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直情應該搭車都唔可以搭有冷氣果D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行路啦!</blockquote><br />\n搭電車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n電車咪又係要用能源，咁唔環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08a6c6d3f20b7d259d9761cff13e87aa83e2d3c","tid":276772,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"佢幾時會燒埋醫院，人應該順應生死，<br />\n<br />\n唔好做手術/治療，浪費資源！"},{"pid":"26ac8fc8dbf96d8e85ec552bb87dd587800ebfc9","tid":276772,"uid":67600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:46:49.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 環保觸覺"},{"pid":"3173285ecaf8c33c16ba64a8aca87033c7c970cb","tid":276772,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:48:17.000Z","msg":"From wiki:<br />\n<br />\n環保觸覺於多年來都有舉辦綠步郊野「慈善」籌款活動，贊助商包括新鴻基地產子公司、恆基地產關聯公司、新世界地產、中華電力和迪士尼樂園等。由於該等贊助商與環保觸覺有直接利益衝突，令外界質疑該組織的日後行動的動機。其中新鴻基地產為馬灣珀麗灣的發展商，而該組織主要負責人譚凱邦就是馬灣區區議員。當區居民認為環保觸覺收取新鴻基地產子公司捐款會令譚在處事上偏幫新鴻基。 加上環保觸覺採取法律行動及司法覆核的項目，大多是針對長實和其他無捐款發展商，甚少與恆基及新鴻基有關。而近年元朗、天水圍一帶的非法泥土山事件中，環保觸覺一直默不作聲，更令人感覺該組織成立目的不是為環保而是藉環保之名騙財。"},{"pid":"8fa7e932beee9657399a5967a1b500f4ba83daac","tid":276772,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>環保撚真係好撚煩<br />\n<br />\n又話咪撚開冷氣？屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/172059_c87e32a46168a2ff835e9ea504a3c203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F172059_c87e32a46168a2ff835e9ea504a3c203.jpg&h=f9ecbdda&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n正呀 有冷氣嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5202fedc2c2f07d13b28d19bd0eb86a29971491","tid":276772,"uid":4422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:55:39.000Z","msg":"間間野食鋪頭都會開冷氣啦 熱到咁唔開點坐得落呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d460d5763e010fbd8b61c34f0386041a6a59689","tid":276772,"uid":807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:04:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>環保撚真係好撚煩<br />\n<br />\n又話咪撚開冷氣？屌你老母<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/172059_c87e32a46168a2ff835e9ea504a3c203.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F172059_c87e32a46168a2ff835e9ea504a3c203.jpg&h=f9ecbdda&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n正呀 有冷氣嘆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n環保觸覺發現部份團體在發佈記者會時，把冷氣溫度調至得十多度，更有嘉賓要著西裝外套。環保觸覺批評，團體在炎夏開冷氣發表記者會，浪費能源，已經去信幾個團體，希望團體到十一月才向市民大眾召開記者會。天文台高級科學主任莫慶炎指，由七月至今，有九日氣溫錄得高達三十三度。而今年七月份平均溫度是29.1度，比過往高了0.4度，呼籲市民節約能源，避免氣候變暖問題繼續惡化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/09/180421_3e6155b953eb09beb30f3770da641fdf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F09%2F180421_3e6155b953eb09beb30f3770da641fdf.jpg&h=c08b7f4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68ca0c13a4be35777d43975700d5d739dd9860f1","tid":276772,"uid":68319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:05:48.000Z","msg":"轟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dc2f4b265c0432c4a85793206259954fa4f17d","tid":276772,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:06:03.000Z","msg":"係就叫晒所有開冷氣既餐廳夏天唔好賣熱食熟食 全部賣生野<br />\n記得最緊要叫譚仔夏天淨係賣凍既清湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b7345932ac072cf2c637a2cceb22c072cce61f","tid":276772,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"環保觸覺轟廚師在炎夏開冷氣煮野食 浪費能源"},{"pid":"9f95e33248aaf9a3cf5885432813e842a7c453d0","tid":276772,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:08:27.000Z","msg":"有供求就有市場嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌黎都哂氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c82e1e97d600ffc37273e6e789d295ae0ec8786","tid":276772,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:13:08.000Z","msg":"你啲能源係潔淨能源嘅話浪費根本冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec209a5bbad91b0cdca0a8ab5bc220027bb013e","tid":276772,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2486ed7fbd30345c34b123d7620b970a4fb0cfb","tid":276772,"uid":38896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:19:36.000Z","msg":"開冷氣打邊爐係on9<br />\n但係我唔打邊爐係咪唔駛開冷氣先 ? <br />\n熱到咁食冷麵都開冷氣啦"},{"pid":"9f939112a412ed7a6c3d8102f0b5bbb47e5a570c","tid":276772,"uid":56447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>on9 咁開冷氣唔好食熱野喇 全部食壽司魚生喇屌你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁樣講好合理<br />\n本身d食物個設計就係咁<br />\n火鍋用黎冬天取暖<br />\n<br />\n咁依家有冷氣當然唔同講法<br />\n但係本身要係咁熱既環境開冷氣已經消耗好多能源<br />\n本身一棟樓既用電量已經有差唔多一半係來自冷氣<br />\n如果你打邊爐係入面整熱曬個空間<br />\n冷氣要用更加多能源去降低個溫度<br />\n如果set十幾度<br />\n真係幾浪費既<br />\n人類係應該思考吓呢d問題<br />\n為個環境著想都好應該</blockquote><br />\n唔啱聽，依度啲人咪鳩屌囉，唔使咁認真</blockquote><br />\non99 咁多工廠日日排廢氣 你唔屌<br />\n就黎屌香港人開大冷氣打邊爐 <br />\n你打少一萬次邊爐都唔及工廠停工一日環保啦</blockquote><br />\n咪係 麻鷹唔捉 捉雞仔 有撚用咩 慳埋比大財團用 有錢人用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6ba516d754427de43a5169e16ec04942d87c8a","tid":276772,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:23:19.000Z","msg":"應該要邊焗桑拿邊打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe419127642e1331f441a368d55d461b34acd42","tid":276772,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"韓燒呢？"},{"pid":"f4542866573d576ebb93490b786eb0e514de5373","tid":276772,"uid":82572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日就著曬羽絨開行冷氣打邊爐"},{"pid":"c52df083ca431c4361c421ab249bae3d31f34930","tid":276772,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:40:23.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post<br />\n決定聽晚打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6aa389afae7c86be3f97adb928a3a085025976","tid":276772,"uid":26672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:41:01.000Z","msg":"佢地班仆街仲喺到獻世就浪費資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />商場冷氣又屌，食下野又屌，喂阿哥打唔打邊爐都要開冷氣架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三十幾度啊屌你，成班友去野外求生啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8ae5d3091bd2d93dc6ff286c26379c6f6c7ce9","tid":276772,"uid":78804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你又臭蟲論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&ldquo;因為工廠仆街啲所以火鍋店仆街唔係問題&ldquo;<br />\n真係叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係咁<br />\n假設你艘船穿左兩個窿<br />\n一大一細<br />\n你會補左大個窿先定細個窿先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點同呀<br />\n依家打邊爐可以大家一齊唔幫襯<br />\n工廠又唔可以逼佢唔開冷氣<br />\n緊係揀有能力改善果個先</blockquote><br />\n普你啊嬤 咪即係恰得就恰"},{"pid":"a494fda414754379a58efc022b49bd8c4d3aeba9","tid":276772,"uid":34665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>on9 咁開冷氣唔好食熱野喇 全部食壽司魚生喇屌你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咁樣講好合理<br />\n本身d食物個設計就係咁<br />\n火鍋用黎冬天取暖<br />\n<br />\n咁依家有冷氣當然唔同講法<br />\n但係本身要係咁熱既環境開冷氣已經消耗好多能源<br />\n本身一棟樓既用電量已經有差唔多一半係來自冷氣<br />\n如果你打邊爐係入面整熱曬個空間<br />\n冷氣要用更加多能源去降低個溫度<br />\n如果set十幾度<br />\n真係幾浪費既<br />\n人類係應該思考吓呢d問題<br />\n為個環境著想都好應該</blockquote><br />\n巴打講得好"},{"pid":"68278691d06725124ed524997acd963aeb5664d5","tid":276772,"uid":34665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你又臭蟲論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&ldquo;因為工廠仆街啲所以火鍋店仆街唔係問題&ldquo;<br />\n真係叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係咁<br />\n假設你艘船穿左兩個窿<br />\n一大一細<br />\n你會補左大個窿先定細個窿先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點同呀<br />\n依家打邊爐可以大家一齊唔幫襯<br />\n工廠又唔可以逼佢唔開冷氣<br />\n緊係揀有能力改善果個先</blockquote><br />\n普你啊嬤 咪即係恰得就恰</blockquote><br />\n呢個係力有所及的問題"},{"pid":"65ff69e07c3b58c0f5c37011c5150572ae0ff416","tid":276772,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:59:05.000Z","msg":"不時不食"},{"pid":"ae29b85711551754756549bbbe34e9f616eae1e4","tid":276772,"uid":88985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:21:40.000Z","msg":"唔好話開冷氣打邊爐喇<br />\n係室内開大冷氣但個個著哂褸已經係浪費<br />\n呢單唔明有咩好反"},{"pid":"390e308864224a885068ce2a0fea00e730c3603e","tid":276772,"uid":19654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:37:27.000Z","msg":"連登仔根本就港豬心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n竟然第一時間關心火鍋店有無生意做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地有冇錢賺關你撚事咩<br />\n夏天開大冷氣打邊盧的確好撚反智喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f67eed4ea9d7b8c0be8232ef3dcf1effdf06ac","tid":276772,"uid":97494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:54:31.000Z","msg":"佢地呢個團體都係浪費緊地球資源"},{"pid":"4a276827eef9a6f375fd4605681ef881a104e0b4","tid":276772,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:55:24.000Z","msg":"環保觸覺一日可以出幾多個膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d3dab10c7e48a8dde48ab0c89b2d1831bd0dcc","tid":276772,"uid":2643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"環保既大前題我覺得係唔影響人類既生活同發展下進行<br />\n如果你覺得因為夏天唔可以開冷氣打邊爐而唔打我唔認同<br />\n即係如果要等period黎先可以性交唔駛浪費套既話，我唔認同<br />\n<br />\n利申 認真左"},{"pid":"0a4ae5f38e4f7a8d90c2109033f0525e2dcc06f5","tid":276772,"uid":85944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"吊咁夏天係咪要日能日食冷麵"},{"pid":"0facb6eaac3aaa877fa383476d8a2e9918b0440f","tid":276772,"uid":48670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你又臭蟲論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&ldquo;因為工廠仆街啲所以火鍋店仆街唔係問題&ldquo;<br />\n真係叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係咁<br />\n假設你艘船穿左兩個窿<br />\n一大一細<br />\n你會補左大個窿先定細個窿先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點同呀<br />\n依家打邊爐可以大家一齊唔幫襯<br />\n工廠又唔可以逼佢唔開冷氣<br />\n緊係揀有能力改善果個先</blockquote><br />\n普你啊嬤 咪即係恰得就恰</blockquote><br />\n呢個係力有所及的問題</blockquote><br />\n呢個係欺善怕惡的問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}